Yes =E2=80=93 don=E2=80=99t think your average CEO sees themselves =
running their company by hand holding.

=20

But they must be wondering =E2=80=9Chow am I going to run my company in =
the new age?

=20

How do I understand where my Ghandi powers are most needed? I =
can=E2=80=99t attack every cultural challenge in every part of my =
business.

How do I keep my culture alive without the office and hierarchical =
structures?

How do I get my cultural messages through without my traditional =
management structures?

If I could only talk to each employee directly they would see my vision =
and love me

I need to know if employees aren=E2=80=99t acting as I would expect =
before it becomes a front page news story or they start to protest

I need a construct to explain to long serving employees how we need to =
change, act and perform in a modern world

And a construct that makes me more nimble to pension off / fire those =
that don=E2=80=99t see and support my vision

=20

They=E2=80=99ll need a combination of new technology and their own SWAT =
team of digital analysts, behavioural experts, ex-cambridge analytica =
content creators and communication experts that report directly to =
them=E2=80=A6=E2=80=A6=E2=80=A6=E2=80=A6=E2=80=A6.

=20

