=E2=80=93 and that it will include a small cadre of senior managers =
sitting in front of screens that tell them what is going on at their =
company =E2=80=93 not just technically but also what is going on with =
their talent / personal capital. They will then pull some levers and =
monitor the impact.

=20

This future of work is obviously key to what we are doing =E2=80=93 =
wonder whether you may have another blog post or article in you that =
